          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXA8Ewfnhih7nk4fM-jl5RkLjlmWkDBbj3_Qn6WQnF_iJCFCsaf=s120-c-rp-mo-br100",
          "description": "Dr, Sandeep Jain and team were so efficient. There were handful of patients when I arrived for my appointment but the team had a efficient flow going so each patient like me was seen in a timely manner. They were organized by having our paperworks on a large envelope with our information & name on it.\n\nWhen it was turn to see the doctor\u2014 I know he was busy but the personable interaction and conversation was still present. So thank you to the team and Dr Sandeep Jain for the smooth process because this road itself is anxiety provoking already but the team ease me in this part of the journey. Thank you!",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tkdWQydEtjV014YzNwSlIxOHhUM0ZNY2w5NlpHYxAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x4e4b88bc80833369!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOkdud2tKcWMxc3pJR18xT3FMcl96ZGc%7C%7C?hl=en",
